sources.title: Sounds of the 70's : Rocking all over the World
sources.description:
This music documentary series dives into the dynamic 1970s, exploring how music mirrored an era of change and upheaval. From bubble-gum pop to the rise of glam rock, hard rock, punk rock, progressive rock, new wave and don't forget disco.  This episode includes legendary performances from Status Quo, T-Rex, The Damned, Peter Tosh with Mick Jagger, The Edgar Winter Group, Roxy Music, Free, 10cc, Suzi Quatro, Sparks, The Stranglers, The Boomtown Rats, & Alice Cooper.


Director: Jason Fenwick
Year 2021
